						 <p>Ah! I get it. He's a reality bender with a god complex. Think about it. He must have really wanted to save his brother right? But he was also incredibly sadistic. So he didn't get much of a rise out of healing people. But when he inadvertently caused that woman all that grief, he not by god, but by his own mental illness. However, he mistook this invigoration for his powers coming back, and the rest is history.</p> <p>Then he got picked up by the foundation and put into a cell.</p> 
				 	]]>
